# Web Push — VAPID public key (safe to expose; this is the public half).
# Generate a keypair with:  npx web-push generate-vapid-keys
# Put the PUBLIC key here, and set the PRIVATE key as a secret in the
# push-api Deno Deploy project (VAPID_PRIVATE_KEY). See push-api/README.md.
VITE_VAPID_PUBLIC_KEY=
